videos.description: Notre Dame works the ball around and gives it to a loosely guarded TJ Gibbs who knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Gibbs gives Irish the lead with a 3) 2020/02/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gibbs gives Irish the lead with a 3

videos.description: Christian Keeling gets the 3-pointer to fall after the Tar Heels went five minutes without a single bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Keeling ends UNC's scoring drought with a 3) 2020/02/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Keeling ends UNC's scoring drought with a 3

videos.description: Jon Mooney backs down his defender to get the lob from Rex Pflueger and he barely touches the ball to get the layup in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Mooney quickly tips in the layup) 2020/02/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mooney quickly tips in the layup

videos.description: Leaky Black tips the ball away and runs it back for a wide-open, one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Black's steal leads to a slam

videos.description: With a defender's hand in his face, Cole Anthony still finds a way to drain the corner 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Anthony knocks down the step-back triple) 2020/02/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anthony knocks down the step-back triple

videos.description: Prentiss Hubb drives down to the bucket and reels in a layup to get fans are on their feet as Notre Dame continues a 10-2 run.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Hubb's layup brings Irish fans to their feet) 2020/02/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hubb's layup brings Irish fans to their feet

videos.description: Nate Laszewski knocks down the game-sealing 3-pointer to save the Irish from falling to North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Laszewski seals the deal with deep 3) 2020/02/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Laszewski seals the deal with deep 3

videos.description: UNC head coach Roy Williams relays frustration about losing another close game but says he doesn't expect his players to give up and wants them to keep fighting.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Williams on 6th-straight loss: ‘You can give in or you can freaking compete’) 2020/02/17

videos.headline: Williams on sixth straight loss: 'You can give in, or you can freaking compete'
